lenders.occupational_info:
Yohan Foods unlike a typical dry chilli pepper processing SME will provide a unique-well packaged powdered chilli pepper processed under a very hygienic condition for the culinary market.  Yohan is the answer to the increasing demand for quality-but-affordable dry chilli products. Consumers want: (1) well packaged bacteria-free powdered chilli processed from crispy raw material, and (2) consumed at a cost that they can afford and in such a way that they will derive lasting memories concerning their recipes. Yohan Foods goal is to provide consumers with the fresh packed powdered chilli pepper that they require.  
This business plan is prepared to obtain financing in the amount of GH¢ 9000. This amount is seventy-two percent (72%) of the total start-up capital. The finance is required to cover raw material cost for the first month, equipment purchase, delivery van repairs and completion of administrative procedures. The additional twenty-eight percent (28%) has already been secured in the form of capital asset from owner John-Rye Adade. 
The financing in addition to the capital contribution from the owner will allow Yohan Foods to successfully open and maintain operations through year one. The large initial capital investment will allow Yohan foods to provide its customers with unique and standard products. Successful operations in year one will provide Yohan Foods with a customer base that will allow it to be self sufficient in year two.

lenders.name: remoteaccesslyt
lenders.occupational_info:
ROAM, or remote operations asset management, is a revolutionary technology that offers new wireless light control. It is a solution to the need for reliability of utility and for safety, security and visual acuity. It allows lighting system managers and operators to quickly detect, repair and manage problems with the lighting systems.
ROAM functions by creating a mesh network throughout all the lighting products in a system. With a photocontrol that is embedded with a wireless communication chip for each lighting fixture, errors can easily be communicated and located. Also, key fixture attributes like lamp type and wattage is captured for easy monitoring and management.
With ROAM, you can maximize material utilization, reduce energy consumption and increase customer satisfaction. It has already enhanced a number of lighting applications with its wireless light control and holds the “Best of Category” award from the LIGHTFAIR 2007.
